<br>
Okay, here we go:<br>
<br>
1) Riposte disciplines keep Venril Sathir from proccing (he procs on almost every hit).  Riposte is a skill that allows you to avoid a hit (reasonable assumption).  Therefore, you can not proc on an avoidance miss.<br>
<br>
2) Weapons can proc on a miss.  Since you can not proc on an avoidance miss (see #1), the miss must have been mitigated (reasonable assumption).<br>
<br>
Comments please.  Yes, there are some assumptions, but I feel that they are minor.<br>
